Q1: What is node.js?

Ans: Node.js is a Server side scripting which is used to build scalable programs.Node.js is an open source server framework, runs on various platforms (Windows, Linux, Unix, Mac OS X, etc.).Its multiple advantages over other server side languages, the prominent being non-blocking I/O.
